{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1976,"month":10,"day":24}],"page_start":5,"page_end":5,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"欢庆的鼓声","authors":["雷抒雁"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"咚咚，咚咚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咚咚，咚咚……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这不是大海的涛声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也不是九天的雷鸣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是鼓声啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢庆的鼓声！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"响在大街小巷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"响在工厂车间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"响在村头田野，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"响在哨所军营……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咚咚，咚咚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咚咚，咚咚……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“欢呼！欢呼！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民在欢庆华国锋同志任主席啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢快的鼓声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"压倒了大海的涛声！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“欢呼，欢呼！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民在欢呼粉碎“四人帮”的胜利啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"激情的锣音，胜过九天的雷鸣！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，这才真正是——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无产者盛大的节日！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看游行的队伍——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千道洪流，万条长龙！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看游行的群众——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满脸笑容，一身轻松！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十月啊，我们的祖国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吹来如此温暖的春风。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"篡权的野心家——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"断了黑手！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骗人的阴谋家——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现了原形！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这帮不肯改悔的走资派，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想当日，人民头上耍尽威风；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看今朝，人民一伸腰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们便滚进了茅坑！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席缔造的党啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"久经烈火锻炼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想要搞垮它，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呸！那是白日做梦！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东思想武装的人民啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"意志比钢铁更硬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁与人民作对，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就让他滚进墓坑！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢庆人民的伟大胜利啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼓，怎能不纵情地敲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锣，怎能不纵情地鸣！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咚咚，咚咚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咚咚，咚咚……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼓声高，阵阵相呼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锣声紧，声声相应！欢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庆伟大的胜利，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们倍感毛主席伟大、英明！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他从群众的眼里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听到人民的心声："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真革命，假革命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民，看得最分明！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他从骗子的行踪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"识破了他们的野心！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在风里，在浪里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为革命把接班人选定！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咚咚，咚咚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢庆的锣鼓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从黎明响到深夜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从深夜又响到黎明！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫要说，前边——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有雨，还有风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的党啊后继有人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们坚信革命必胜！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"团结在以华国锋同志为首的党中央周"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"围，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们铁臂相挽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"筑一道攻不破的长城！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟着以华国锋同志为首的党中央前进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们脚步铿锵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狂风恶浪撼不动！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咚咚，咚咚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咚咚，咚咚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这难道只是鼓声吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不，是我们祖国亿万颗心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在兴奋地一齐跳动！"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"华国锋","type":"人物"},{"name":"党内资产阶级","type":"主题/事件"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}